      "comment": "LONE RUSTLER (7) failed to feature last start after missing the jump at Gunnedah, but prior to that won by one length at this track (19.17) beating Dana Curly in a Grade 5 on April 1. Can discover winning form. LET'S GO OUT (2) racing well without winning, placing at her last four runs. Last start finished 2nd in a Grade 4 on April 1 over 330m at this track behind Nangar Mcgraw beaten 4 lengths (18.74). Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to her name from five starts. Expecting another good run. PIGEON'S DESIRE (4) has a strong record this trip with 32 wins and 19 placings from 71 starts. Missed the frame latest (19.23) when fifth over 330m at this track in a NG. Can hit the frame with the right run. ASCEND JACARANDA (3) has strong claims after a top-three finish at this track and distance last time out.",
